{{Databox|fr=Pythagore}}'''Pitaguras''' (570 - 495 Q.M) iga yan ufaylasuf d amassan n [[tusnakt]] agriki, d nttan ay bdan amussu apitagori xklli s tussan tanfalit nns (nadarya n Putaguras). Lkmnaɣd inɣmissn fllas zɣ idlisn ittyuran dffir tasutin f tamttant nns, ɣayn af iqqand ad nssen masd ur llan umlan iṣḥan izdin d tmamkt n uswingm nns d twuri nns. Ilul ɣ tagzirt n [[Samus]] ilmma imudda s tmizar yaḍnin zund [[Agrik]] d [[Miṣra|Miṣṛa]] d ḥaqqan [[Lhnd]] ula nttat.

